  "short_description": "Climb, FALL, Die! is the theme of Axium's Box, a game that draws inspiration from \"Celeste\" and \"Jump King,\" while taking it to a whole new level with stunning 3D graphics. If you enjoy pain, frustration, challenging obstacles, and, paradigm shifts then Axium's Box is the game for you.",
